                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "AnimationTags"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "[LOGAN] Astarion stops walking and embraces his ascension to Sun King. The crowd is enamoured. An NPC reaches out to Astarion, who appears like a messiah. The Nobleman is watching."}
