                                 },
                                 {
                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "CinematicNodeContext"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "Astarion's body now blazes like the noonday sun. He has become the Sun King of the city, his head wreathed in a fiery crown. A small crowd watches on in awe - most notably, a young NOBLEMAN."}
                                 },
