                        "constructor" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "TagAnswer"},
                        "editorData" : [
                           {
                              "data" : [
                                 {
                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "AnimationTags"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "[LOGAN] NPC's are panicking, standing up, reacting where they are. In the dark we see the approaching sillhouttes of vampires. The nobleman, having seen the mist, spins back to Astarion in fear. Astarion's still outstretched hand offers him hope - he gestures with a suave, devilish tilt forward of the head and movement of the hand. Nobleman is won over completely; he approaches, reaching for the hand. As soon as their fingertips touch Astarion yanks him. The nobleman is swiftly twisted around as if in a lover's impassioned dance., , Astarion takes in the submissive Nobleman's neck, drinking in his smell. Astarion's head lifts high before his eyes and fangs flash and he takes a plunge into the nobleman's neck., , A pinned noble resists to no avail. Astarion keeps steadily draining. The struggle ends; a limp body is held., , , [AMN] Action and silhouette very important here., "}
                                 },
                                 {
                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "Attitude"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "Default"}
                                 },
                                 {
                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "CinematicNodeContext"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "Back to the young NOBLEMAN, who shrinks from the darkness and turns to Astarion, hope in his eyes. Astarion smiles and beckons him forward into the light - before laughing and digging his fangs into the boy's neck. (NOTE: Both Astarion and nobleman's silhouettes needs to be very clear here)"}
                                 },
