                              "data" : [
                                 {
                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "AnimationTags"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "[LOGAN] Shots of NPC's in awe, looking at the Noble - they can't believe he's so lucky to be chosen. A lamp flickers; a bell might toll. One man turns around in the alleyway. He sees the mist begin to approach. A woman turns round after him too, and both react scared and confused."}
                                 },
                                 {
                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "Attitude"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "Default"}
                                 },
                                 {
                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "CinematicNodeContext"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "In the distance, screams. A wide shot over the city shows mists rolling through the streets, quenching all light. Where the mists pass, the blazing red eyes of vampire spawn bloom in the shadows. \r\nSoon the city is shrouded in darkness but for the single blazing beacon that is Astarion."}
                                 },
